1. *Minut* je trajao večno. (The minute lasted forever.)
2. Sada je *minuta* za pauzu. (It's now time for a break.)
3. *Minutu* pre mog odlaska, on je stigao. (One minute before my departure, he arrived.)
4. Za *minut* ću biti spreman. (In a minute I will be ready.)
5. U *minutu* je sve to završeno. (It was all done in a minute.)